o Urdin - Biography and Self Portrait _ 10"></a></span><span class="post-image"><a href="http://kirourdin.info/wp-content/uploads/2011/11/about_14.jpg" class="fancy"  rel="group1"><img src="http://kirourdin.info/wp-content/uploads/2011/11/about_14.jpg" height="240" width="172" class="slide" offset="-3325" title="Kiro Urdin - Biography and Self Portrait _ 11"  alt="Kiro Urdin - Biography and Self Portrait _ 11"></a></span><span class="post-image"><a href="http://kirourdin.info/wp-content/uploads/2011/11/about_15.jpg" class="fancy"  rel="group1"><img src="http://kirourdin.info/wp-content/uploads/2011/11/about_15.jpg" height="240" width="505" class="slide" offset="-3846" title="Kiro Urdin - Biography and Self Portrait _ 12"  alt="Kiro Urdin - Biography and Self Portrait _ 12"></a></span>		</div>		
				
		
				
